dc_title_s: Map of the Colony and Protectorate of Nigeria, 1933
dc_description_s: Map shows international, provincial, and Mandated Territory boundaries, provincial and divisional headquarters, towns and villages, railways in operation and under construction, and all-season and dry-season roads. "Drawn & Reproduced by Nigeria Surveys, Lagos Dec. 1933." Original map is filed in the Map and Geospatial Information Center. A map reproduction is attached to companion volume. Map shows international, provincial, and mandated territory boundaries, provincial and divisional headquarters, towns and villages, railways in operation and under construction, and all-season and dry-season roads.
